# EUCS IDAM End User Guidance

Access user guides, technical advice, and Identity and Access Management (IdAM) policies. Use this page to raise service requests and queries.

## Service Requests

If your query does not match the requests below, email the **[EUCS IDAM Team](mailto:idam@justice.gov.uk)**.

| Category | Task | How to raise the request |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Account Management** | Add user account (MOJO Production) | [Request new user account](https://mojprod.service-now.com/moj_sp?id=sc_cat_item&table=sc_cat_item&sys_id=7404ac3137b723005f7cd1b543990e3e&searchTerm=SERVICE%20ACCOUNT) |
| | Delete user account (MOJO Production) | [Request account deletion](https://mojprod.service-now.com/moj_sp?id=sc_cat_item&table=sc_cat_item&sys_id=c195e78edb73e7441b4ffc45ae9619f2&searchTerm=SERVICE%20ACCOUNT) |
| | Request service account (MOJO Production) | [Request service account access](https://mojprod.service-now.com/moj_sp?id=sc_cat_item&table=sc_cat_item&sys_id=2ab6ea321b142a9025dc6351f54bcb15&recordUrl=com.glideapp.servicecatalog_cat_item_view.do%3Fv%3D1&sysparm_id=2ab6ea321b142a9025dc6351f54bcb15) |
| | Add or remove guest account (MOJO Production) | Email the [EUCS IDAM Team](mailto:idam@justice.gov.uk) |
| | Add or remove privileged account (MOJO LIVE, NLE, or DEV) | [Manage privileged account](https://mojprod.service-now.com/moj_sp?id=sc_cat_item&table=sc_cat_item&sys_id=8161246a1b170a50a1e2ddf0b24bcbdb&searchTerm=SERVICE%20ACCOUNT) |
| | Add or remove privileged account (DOM1 Dev / NLE) | Email the [EUCS IDAM Team](mailto:idam@justice.gov.uk) |
| **Application Consent** | Approve delegated application consent | Request via a formal demand for business justification review. [Follow demand guidance](https://justiceuk.sharepoint.com/sites/DemandandBusinessRelationshipManagement/SitePages/New-Demand-Request.aspx) |
| **Security Groups** | Add or remove a user | Group owners perform these tasks. If the owner is unavailable, email the [EUCS IDAM Team](mailto:idam@justice.gov.uk) |
| | Create a new security group | Raise a demand request. [Follow demand guidance](https://justiceuk.sharepoint.com/sites/DemandandBusinessRelationshipManagement/SitePages/New-Demand-Request.aspx) |
| **Access Packages** | Add, amend, or delete a user | [Manage access package user](https://mojprod.service-now.com/moj_sp?id=sc_cat_item&table=sc_cat_item&sys_id=8161246a1b170a50a1e2ddf0b24bcbdb&searchTerm=SERVICE%20ACCOUNT) |
| | Create or amend an access package | [Submit new demand request](https://justiceuk.sharepoint.com/sites/DemandandBusinessRelationshipManagement/SitePages/New-Demand-Request.aspx) |
| | Create custom roles or service principals | [Submit new demand request](https://justiceuk.sharepoint.com/sites/DemandandBusinessRelationshipManagement/SitePages/New-Demand-Request.aspx) |
| **Single Sign-On** | Create an application registration | [Submit new demand request](https://justiceuk.sharepoint.com/sites/DemandandBusinessRelationshipManagement/SitePages/New-Demand-Request.aspx) or [use self-service registration](https://www.google.com/search?q=/documentation/guidance/selfserveappreg.html) |
| | Delete an application registration | [Submit new demand request](https://justiceuk.sharepoint.com/sites/DemandandBusinessRelationshipManagement/SitePages/New-Demand-Request.aspx) |
| | Renew secret or certificate | [Renew Entra ID certificate/secret](https://www.google.com/search?q=https://mojprod.service-now.com/moj_sp%3Fid%3Dsc_cat_item%26table%3Dsc_cat_item%26sys_id%3D1c192ec11b930a10a1e2ddf0b24bcb77). Application owners can update secrets directly. |
| **Multi-Factor Authentication** | Manage MFA tokens | Use the [Technology Portal](https://www.google.com/search?q=https://mojprod.service-now.com/moj_sp) to assign or delete tokens. |

